            {
               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><svg width=\"450\" height=\"100\"  fill=\"none\" stroke=\"black\"> <defs> <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"5\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\"> <path d=\"M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z\" /></marker> </defs> <line x1=\"2\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"440\" y2=\"15\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\" /> <text x=\"0\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">0</text> <text x=\"40\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">1</text> <text x=\"80\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">2</text> <text x=\"120\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">3</text> <text x=\"160\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">4</text> <text x=\"200\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">5</text> <text x=\"240\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">6</text> <text x=\"280\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">7</text> <text x=\"320\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">8</text> <text x=\"360\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">9</text> <text x=\"400\" y=\"40\" font-size=\"1.5em\">10</text> <line x1=\"5\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"5\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"45\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"45\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"85\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"85\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"125\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"125\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"165\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"165\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"205\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"205\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"245\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"245\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"285\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"285\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"325\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"325\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"365\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"365\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" /> <line x1=\"410\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"410\" y2=\"25\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"3\" />  </svg></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Graph 1</b>: Representation of a path.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "Now, compare it with **Figure 1**, which presents a utensil used in the kitchen of the Shona culture (<htcite0>).",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "cc162709-bdc3-469b-a208-e900f4570842",
